00:38:51.197 --> 00:38:53.030
MICHAEL SHORT: So you
said it's because it's

00:38:53.030 --> 00:38:55.197
the biggest source of energy
that could be released?

00:38:55.197 --> 00:38:58.398
AUDIENCE: Well, it seems to
