00:39:22.480 --> 00:39:23.438
MICHAEL SHORT: Exactly.

00:39:23.438 --> 00:39:26.800
So the question with this is,
what do we have to conserve?

00:39:26.800 --> 00:39:28.870
Mass momentum energy charge.

00:39:28.870 --> 00:39:32.350
If we have platinum-192
go into platinum-192,

00:39:32.350 --> 00:39:34.960
the mass is pretty
much the same.

00:39:34.960 --> 00:39:35.460
Yep.

00:39:35.460 --> 00:39:36.020
Question, Luke?

00:39:36.020 --> 00:39:37.510
AUDIENCE: What does it
mean to put platinum

00:39:37.510 --> 00:39:38.635
in the excited [INAUDIBLE]?

00:39:38.635 --> 00:39:42.412
MICHAEL SHORT: It means it's at
