We've only had one explosion.

01:07:07.120 --> 01:07:08.890
There was no
temperature at the time,

01:07:08.890 --> 01:07:11.290
but it sounded like
a shotgun blast

01:07:11.290 --> 01:07:12.910
over the side of your shoulder.

