they're approaching

01:07:36.850 --> 01:07:38.022
close to their rated thing.

01:07:38.022 --> 01:07:38.980
And you're like, great.

01:07:38.980 --> 01:07:39.897
It's at half pressure.

01:07:39.897 --> 01:07:40.720
It's OK.

